code: @Override protected void doStart() throws Exception {     super.doStart().     if (!canConnected) {         // if we cannot connect then its due to clash on context-path when using Jetty         String msg = "Cannot bind this Camel Jetty consumer to the JettyServer connector as there is already an existing Camel Jetty consumer using the same context-path: " + getPath().         throw new IllegalStateException(msg).     } }
